law.text:
This subtitle does not apply to an advertisement, offer to sell, retail sale, or wholesale sale, if the merchandise:
Is sold in a bona fide clearance sale and is so advertised and marked;
Must be sold promptly in order to prevent loss;
Is imperfect, damaged, or being discontinued and is so advertised and marked;
Is sold on the final liquidation of a business;
Is sold for charitable purposes or to relief agencies;
Is sold on contract to a department of a government or governmental institution;
Is sold by an officer acting under the order or direction of a court;
Is sold at a price set in good faith to meet competition; or
Is motor fuel sold by a retail service station dealer.
